    {
      "para_id": "p1",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 1,
      "text": "Subject: The Deterioration of Video Game Standards and the Exploitative Nature of Microtransactions",
      "char_len": 99,
      "chunk_word_count": 13,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9885057471264368,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8787878787878788
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.4566570881226054,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p2",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 2,
      "text": "Summary:",
      "char_len": 8,
      "chunk_word_count": 1,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.875,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 1.0
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.35625,
        "flags": [
          "very_short"
        ]
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p3",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 3,
      "text": "The modern video game industry, once driven by creative excellence and fair consumer value, has seen a marked decline in product quality due to the proliferation of microtransactions (MTX). These practices have introduced hidden costs, manipulated user behavior, and created a marketplace that increasingly resembles a digital casino, particularly harming children and vulnerable consumers.",
      "char_len": 390,
      "chunk_word_count": 54,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.973293768545994,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8641025641025641
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.9799703264094956,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p4",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 4,
      "text": "Decline in Product Standards",
      "char_len": 28,
      "chunk_word_count": 4,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 1.0,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8928571428571429
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.45,
        "flags": [
          "very_short"
        ]
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p5",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 5,
      "text": "In the past, consumers paid a flat fee for a full, complete game. Today, many games launch unfinished or with key features deliberately withheld to be sold later through paid updates or in-game purchases. This practice encourages developers to prioritize monetization over quality or innovation.",
      "char_len": 295,
      "chunk_word_count": 45,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9721115537848606,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8508474576271187
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.933250332005312,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p6",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 6,
      "text": "Examples: Broken launches (e.g., Cyberpunk 2077, Battlefield 2042), lack of meaningful content at release, and dependency on post-launch \"seasons\" or DLC to complete the experience.",
      "char_len": 181,
      "chunk_word_count": 26,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.8662420382165605,
        "digit": 0.050955414012738856,
        "non_space": 0.8674033149171271
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.5635704175513093,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p7",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 7,
      "text": "Result: Consumers pay more for less content, often receiving a product that is technically or creatively inferior to past generations.",
      "char_len": 134,
      "chunk_word_count": 20,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9739130434782609,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8582089552238806
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.5526570048309178,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p8",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 8,
      "text": "Microtransactions as a Hidden Cost",
      "char_len": 34,
      "chunk_word_count": 5,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 1.0,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8823529411764706
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.45,
        "flags": [
          "very_short"
        ]
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p9",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 9,
      "text": "MTX systems are designed to extract ongoing payments from users beyond the initial purchase price. These are often hidden behind complex in-game economies and predatory psychological triggers.",
      "char_len": 192,
      "chunk_word_count": 27,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9819277108433735,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8645833333333334
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.6656124497991969,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p10",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 10,
      "text": "Loot boxes, gacha systems, and premium currencies mimic gambling mechanics.",
      "char_len": 75,
      "chunk_word_count": 10,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9545454545454546,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.88
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.41590909090909095,
        "flags": [
          "very_short"
        ]
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p11",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 11,
      "text": "Players spend money without clear knowledge of what they will receive – similar to slot machines.",
      "char_len": 97,
      "chunk_word_count": 15,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.975609756097561,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.845360824742268
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.47754065040650406,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p12",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 12,
      "text": "Cosmetic or progression-based MTX pressures players into paying for status, competitiveness, or basic enjoyment, creating a \"pay-to-win\" environment or social exclusion for those who don't pay.",
      "char_len": 193,
      "chunk_word_count": 27,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9404761904761905,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8704663212435233
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.6345238095238095,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p13",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 13,
      "text": "Result: These hidden costs can exceed the original purchase price many times over and are intentionally obfuscated through complex pricing (e.g., virtual currency conversions, bundles).",
      "char_len": 185,
      "chunk_word_count": 26,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9503105590062112,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8702702702702703
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.6266218081435473,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p14",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 14,
      "text": "Psychological Exploitation &amp; Youth Vulnerability",
      "char_len": 52,
      "chunk_word_count": 5,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9583333333333334,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.9230769230769231
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.41875,
        "flags": [
          "very_short"
        ]
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p15",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 15,
      "text": "Many of these monetization strategies exploit psychological principles such as: Variable rewards (like those found in gambling)",
      "char_len": 127,
      "chunk_word_count": 17,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.972972972972973,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8740157480314961
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.5061186186186186,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p16",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 16,
      "text": "FOMO (Fear of Missing Out) through limited-time offers or battle passes Social pressure to conform via cosmetic purchases",
      "char_len": 121,
      "chunk_word_count": 18,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9711538461538461,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.859504132231405
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.5200320512820513,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p17",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 17,
      "text": "Younger players are especially vulnerable. Many do not fully grasp the real-world value of money when converted into in-game currencies, leading to reckless or compulsive spending.",
      "char_len": 180,
      "chunk_word_count": 26,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.967741935483871,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8611111111111112
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.6396953405017922,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p18",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 18,
      "text": "According to studies and lawsuits, children have spent thousands of dollars unknowingly.",
      "char_len": 88,
      "chunk_word_count": 12,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.974025974025974,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.875
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.4305194805194805,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p19",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 19,
      "text": "In countries like Belgium and the Netherlands, loot boxes have already been legally classified as a form of gambling.",
      "char_len": 117,
      "chunk_word_count": 19,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9797979797979798,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8461538461538461
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.5417929292929293,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p20",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 20,
      "text": "A Call for Regulation",
      "char_len": 21,
      "chunk_word_count": 4,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 1.0,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8571428571428571
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.45,
        "flags": [
          "very_short"
        ]
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p21",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 21,
      "text": "If traditional gambling, children's advertising, and financial services are regulated to protect consumers, especially minors, then the video game industry - which now outpaces both film and music in revenue - deserves the same scrutiny.",
      "char_len": 237,
      "chunk_word_count": 33,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9605911330049262,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8565400843881856
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.741276683087028,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p22",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 22,
      "text": "Suggested actions:",
      "char_len": 18,
      "chunk_word_count": 2,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9411764705882353,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.9444444444444444
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.40588235294117647,
        "flags": [
          "very_short"
        ]
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p23",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 23,
      "text": "Transparency laws requiring clear display of real-world prices",
      "char_len": 62,
      "chunk_word_count": 8,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9818181818181818,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8870967741935484
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.4363636363636364,
        "flags": [
          "very_short"
        ]
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p24",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 24,
      "text": "Ban or restrict loot box mechanics and gambling-like features for minors",
      "char_len": 72,
      "chunk_word_count": 11,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9838709677419355,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8611111111111112
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.43790322580645163,
        "flags": [
          "very_short"
        ]
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p25",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 25,
      "text": "Refund rights for digital purchases and in-game items",
      "char_len": 53,
      "chunk_word_count": 8,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9782608695652174,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8679245283018868
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.4336956521739131,
        "flags": [
          "very_short"
        ]
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p26",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 26,
      "text": "Mandate completion - games sold as \"complete\" must meet certain functionality",
      "char_len": 77,
      "chunk_word_count": 10,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9552238805970149,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8701298701298701
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.4164179104477612,
        "flags": [
          "very_short"
        ]
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p27",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 27,
      "text": "standards on release",
      "char_len": 20,
      "chunk_word_count": 3,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 1.0,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.9
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.45,
